{
  "texts": [
    "FPB is used as resource for finan-cial sentiment analysis, especially for training and benchmarking models in the financial domain.",
    "For evaluation, we prompted the language models to output the sentiment of each sample, given the choices positive, negative, and neutral.",
    "The Financial Phrase Bank (FPB) dataset is licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 3.0 Unported (CC BY-NC-SA 3.0) License.",
    "The Zero-Shot prompt used for FPB is given in Figure 16.",
    "Zero-Shot Prompt \"\"\" Discard all the previous instructions."
  ]
}